Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.77,0:01:33.36,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Left Burner... \N Flame pressure increasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.88,0:01:36.53,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me all you've got, Phantom Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.53,0:01:38.28,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Left Burner...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.28,0:01:39.66,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,230000...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.66,0:01:40.87,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,240000...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.69,0:01:43.37,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Entering red zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.45,0:01:50.00,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Gauge symmetry,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.95,0:01:52.21,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Standby to fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.61,0:01:54.42,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes, Phantom Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:18.38,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Přestaň se vychloubat, ty malý spratku!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.38,0:02:20.41,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Chceš po mě, abych na tebe šel vším, co mám?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.95,0:02:24.70,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobrá, ukážu ti svou skutečnou sílu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.93,0:02:28.94,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Vystřel, rychle Vongolo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.94,0:02:34.46,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemůžeš udržet rovnováhu napořád, když už dokončils přípravy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.44,0:02:49.85,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Mlžný typ, Nejvyšší rank,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.85,0:02:52.32,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Ossa Impressione Pekelný Prsten.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.32,0:02:58.15,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Obětuju se peklu, jestli to bude znamenat tvou porážku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.64,0:03:02.96,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Nejsilnější meč, který zanechal Keinihhi, Spettrale Spada.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:09.95,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Jedno z mistrovských děl Keinihhiových brnění, Nebbia Numero Due.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.61,0:03:15.59,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Vyením všechno, všechno abych získal skutečnou sílu,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.22,0:03:17.70,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Sílu Pekla.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.14,0:03:24.16,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Půjdemě do pekla společně, Vongolo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:25.88,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,To je...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:30.07,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Co...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.07,0:03:31.05,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,...to je?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:39.43,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Síla Plamenů dosáhla svého limitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.43,0:03:40.95,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Jestli to bude pokračovat, bude těžké to udržet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.46,0:03:43.11,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím rychle vystřel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.74,0:03:51.88,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Musím tě porazit za každou cenu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.88,0:03:55.06,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Tady teprve začíná pravý teror a hrůza!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.06,0:03:56.55,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Jestli ne...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.55,0:03:58.24,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Porazím tě...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.24,0:04:00.66,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,...Má pravá loajalita nebude nikdy naplněna.{TLC: these three lines make no sense together.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.66,0:04:03.22,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,...Sním tvé tlukucí srdce...{TLC this too along with the above three - maybe it should be "swallow"?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:05.80,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty tvé prokleté oči...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:08.56,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,...Stáhnu tě do pekla.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:09.89,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,...překonám to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.89,0:04:12.77,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Konečné vítězství bude mé.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.70,0:04:20.48,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak co na to říkáš? Tohle je má skutečná síla.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:23.21,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Neříkejte mi, že... \Tohle je také iluze?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.21,0:04:27.87,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Možná, ale jestli není, tak máme opravdové potíže.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.87,0:04:30.41,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Není to reálná iluze,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.41,0:04:32.81,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,ani iluze v realitě.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.81,0:04:35.78,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,mezi těmi dvěma, je jenom jedivá pravda,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.78,0:04:37.25,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,a to je tvá porážka!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.79,0:04:40.57,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Boj se a plač!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.57,0:04:44.72,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Obklopím tě strachem a stáhnu tě do pekla!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.46,0:04:47.18,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Jediný, kdo půjde do pekla, budeš ty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:48.68,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty parchante!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:50.26,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Ukaž mi všechno, co dovedeš.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:56.81,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,To je zlé, jestli to bude pokračovat, Vongolovo tělo neustojí sílu toho plamene.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:05:01.57,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Neboj se, Tsuna už nebude dále čekat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.57,0:05:03.82,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Jdi do pekla!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:05.53,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty jsi jediný...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:08.66,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,jediný, s kým nikdy neprohraju!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.99,0:05:15.46,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,X-Burner Hyper Exploze!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.35,0:05:33.43,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Cože!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.04,0:05:44.70,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Neeeee!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.70,0:05:45.74,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Parchante!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.33,0:05:48.09,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Je ještě příliš brzy, abyste se radovali!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.09,0:05:50.81,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakonec, vy všichni...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.81,0:05:57.12,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,vy všichni jste jenom loutky, které ovládá Byakuran-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.05,0:06:03.17,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Dokázal to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.21,0:06:08.22,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Mořští slimáci?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:12.68,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Vypadá to, že tento obranný blok je vyroben z nich pro zesílení pevnosti a odolnosti{orig: to reinforce the structure}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:16.38,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,To je...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.38,0:06:17.46,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.25,0:06:20.40,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale ne... \N I'm doomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:29.82,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Vongolo...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.69,0:06:47.30,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Díky, Vongolo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.66,0:06:50.47,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobrá práce, Tsuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.45,0:06:52.49,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.34,0:06:58.60,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Po použití své finální síly byl Přízračný Rytíř schopný utéct z expolze.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:06:59.98,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,To mi dělá starosti.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:03.31,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,T-to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.49,0:07:23.61,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,To je...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:48.11,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Jsme tady.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.56,0:07:49.53,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Ano.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:56.81,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Tohle je náš cíl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.81,0:07:58.99,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Ano, Shoichiho zařízení.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:08:03.37,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Budeme se skutečně moci vrátit do našeho světa, když to zničíme?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.76,0:08:06.11,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Kdo ví? Nejdříve si to musíme potvrdit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:11.88,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Jestli je tohleto skutečně spojené s tím, že jsme deset let v budoucnosti.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.65,0:08:14.30,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Vědět to bude víc, než dost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:15.76,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Počkej.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:19.97,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Nečekal jsem, že porazíš Přízračného Rytíře. To bylo dalece za mými výpočty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:21.68,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawado Tsunayoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.32,0:08:25.44,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:29.35,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Irie Shoichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.35,0:08:31.94,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Počkej chvíli, Sawado Tsunayoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:34.95,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Vy obě jste z Cervella...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:37.87,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Proč jste s Irie Shoichim?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.34,0:08:42.04,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Nejprve skloň své zbraně, a pak si budeme moci promluvit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:43.87,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Promluvit?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.32,0:08:48.47,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Přesně tak, chci si s tebou nejdříve o něčem na chvíli promluvit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.47,0:08:49.85,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,O čem se mnou chceš mluvit?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.85,0:08:51.43,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Neslyšel jsi mě snad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.43,0:08:54.09,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Říkal jsem ti, ať nejprve skloníš své zbraně.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.75,0:08:57.74,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Jestli uvidím jediný pokus o odporování,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.74,0:08:59.56,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,tak přijdou o své životy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:08.36,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Všichni!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.79,0:09:11.21,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Irie, co jsi jim to udělal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:12.66,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Uspal jsem je, to je vše.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.66,0:09:13.61,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Uspal?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.29,0:09:19.50,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Kvůli jejich zuřivosti a hlouposti, utrpěla tahle základna těžké poškození.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:24.16,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,POužil jsem zeď vyztuženou materiálem, který je odolný vůči Plamenům Umírající Vůle abych je zahnal do slepé uličky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:28.08,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Když nemohli uniknout, použil jsem uspávací plyn, abych je omráčil.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.78,0:09:31.30,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Nicméně!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:36.21,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Jestli uděláš jakýkoliv neuvážený pohyb, použijeme jiný druh plynu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.37,0:09:40.81,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Jakmile zmáčknu tohle tlačítko, okamžitě zemřou.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:43.27,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:47.15,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Jestli je chceš zachránit, udělej co říkám,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.15,0:09:48.40,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawado Tsunayoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.01,0:09:55.83,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, udělejte to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.83,0:09:57.11,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Ano, pane.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:09:58.36,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Co to děláš?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.73,0:10:02.08,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Žádnou paniku, jenom neutralizuju uspávací plyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.55,0:10:05.75,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Dívej se pozorně. Brzy se probudí.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.29,0:10:25.22,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakra, bolí mě hlava.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.16,0:10:28.11,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Jaková příšerná noční můra.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.11,0:10:30.94,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Já jsem napadl Desátého...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.77,0:10:34.19,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Kde... to jsme?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.67,0:10:36.68,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyou-san... a Chrome-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.68,0:10:37.86,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Všichni!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:39.57,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,T-to je...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:41.03,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Desátý!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.03,0:10:43.19,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Desátý— au!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:46.00,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,C-co je to?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:48.93,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Chytili nás?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:55.13,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to zbytečné. Ta kapsule se fyzickou silou nerozbije.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:57.44,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Ženské z Cervello...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.44,0:10:58.30,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Proč jste tady?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:11:01.64,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Vaše životy jsou pod naší kontrolou.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.19,0:11:04.10,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Bude lepší, když nebudete jednat neuváženě.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:05.68,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Irie Shoichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:08.97,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Musíme si promluvit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.97,0:11:11.34,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Mohli byste se zatím uklidnit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.34,0:11:14.46,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Mluvit? Chceš mluvit, po tom, co jsi nás tady zamkl?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.46,0:11:15.90,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,To je vtip!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.59,0:11:18.28,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Moje Scránka je pryč!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:20.74,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Můj Prsten také...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:23.53,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Odpor je zbytečný.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.53,0:11:26.45,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Všechny vaše Prsteny a Schránky...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:30.16,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,jsem vám zabavil.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.58,0:11:32.17,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Cože!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:35.34,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,T-to je zlé. V takové situaci...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:37.76,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawado!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.29,0:11:39.88,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevšímej si nás. Udělej to!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:40.98,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Lal...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.98,0:11:43.09,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Znič to zařízení!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:47.72,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,To je pravda, Desátý!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:52.02,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,To kruhové zařítzení, jestli ho zničíš, budeme se moci vrátit do minulosti!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:54.10,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Nás si nevšímej!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:54.94,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Ne...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:55.48,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Cože?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.22,0:11:59.11,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Stále si ceníš svého života v této situaci?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:01.57,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Ne, ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:05.78,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Upřímně, tvá ignorace mě skutečně uráží.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.29,0:12:09.70,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Jestli zničíš tohle zařízení, tak to budeš ty, kdo bude mít problémy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:11.12,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,O čem to mluvíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.98,0:12:13.26,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Podívej se.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:17.46,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Podívej se na vlastní oči.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.46,0:12:20.06,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Uvnitř tohoto zařízení jsou...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.06,0:12:24.59,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Ti, se kterými jste si vyměnili místa po střelení Desetiletou Bazukou.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:27.60,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,TO jsou naše budoucí já.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.22,0:12:35.65,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,My z této doby?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:41.50,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Přesně tak. Ale to co vidíte právě teď jsou pouhe hologramy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.17,0:12:45.67,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Ve skutečnosti těla vás z této doby...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.67,0:12:50.35,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Byly rozloženy na molekurární částečky a jsou uchovány uvnitř tohoto přístroje.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:56.50,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Ikdyž jsem vám to moc nevysvětlil, nemusím ti snad říkat, co se stane, když zničíš tohle zařízení.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:58.78,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,C-co se stane?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.78,0:13:01.21,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Neměly se snad naše já z této doby...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:03.76,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,vyměnit pomocí efektu Desetileté bazuky...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:05.68,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,neměly by teď být v naší době před deseti lety?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.68,0:13:07.46,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Přesně tak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.46,0:13:10.85,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,V reálu každý, kdo je zasažen Desetiletou Bazukou
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.15,0:13:14.95,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,se vymění s desetiletou verzí sebe sama z budoucnosti.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:18.06,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale díky tomuto zařízení,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.06,0:13:22.95,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,jsme zabránili vašim desetiletým já vrátit se do minulosti a zůstat tam.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.67,0:13:28.20,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,kdyby totiž vaše desetileté já cestovaly zpátky do minulosti a změnily tam cokoliv,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.76,0:13:32.20,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,mohlo by to způsobit zmatky v Politice 7³.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.77,0:13:36.29,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Politice 7³?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.69,0:13:41.00,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Počkat, ty dokonce víš o Desetileté Bazuce? Neříkej mi, že...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:46.22,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže ten, kdo použil Desetiletou Bazuku a střelil nás...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.91,0:13:48.05,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Tos byl ty?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.44,0:13:50.67,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Přesně tak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.56,0:13:57.77,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,P-padá to přímo na tebe, Reborne!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:01.69,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,To je zlé. Nemůžu se pohnout.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.16,0:14:10.41,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Reborna zasáhla Desetiletá Bazuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.51,0:14:15.15,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.15,0:14:16.21,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Reborne?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:17.45,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Kde jsi, Reborne?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:20.38,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,No, nejsem si jistý, co se to děje,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:22.53,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,ale měl by být zpátky za pět minut.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.28,0:14:28.82,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Před deseti lety, jsem použil technologii z této doby,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.82,0:14:31.43,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,aby tě Desetiletá Bazuka mohla zasáhnout.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.54,0:14:35.06,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Například v případě toho Arcobalena,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.06,0:14:39.54,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,když jsou vystaveni 7³, jejich těla se nebudou moci hýbat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.54,0:14:44.28,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Rozumím, proto jsem měl tehdy pocit, jako by mi ztuhlo mé tělo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.08,0:14:45.94,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale proč?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:50.95,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Proč bys procházel všemi těmito těžkostmi, jen abys nás dostal do této doby?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.14,0:14:53.58,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím odpověz!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.03,0:14:56.65,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Chceš to vědět? Myslím že ano...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.65,0:14:58.72,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Irie-sama, už nic neříkejte.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.72,0:15:00.12,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Ne, odpovím mu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.69,0:15:02.08,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to jednoduché.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.78,0:15:06.19,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Byakuran-san chce zničit tento svět
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.19,0:15:08.90,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,a vytvořit nový.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.90,0:15:11.72,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Z toho důvodu je potřeba Vongolských Prstenů.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.08,0:15:13.55,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Vongolských Prstenů?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.05,0:15:18.48,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,V tomto světě existuje spousta prstenů se skrytou silou.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:22.02,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Nicméně, mezi nimi jsou Vongolské a Mořské Prsteny speciální.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.68,0:15:24.80,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Sedm Vongolských prstenů,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.80,0:15:26.94,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Sedm Mořských prstenů,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.94,0:15:30.30,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,a sedm dudlíků Arcobalen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.30,0:15:34.16,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Sedm z nich od každého dělá dohromady 21 Prstenů,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:36.04,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Které jsou ve skutečnosti známé jako 7³.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.94,0:15:44.34,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Jádra 7³ jsou základními kameny, které stvořily tento svět.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:51.97,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Jak to může být...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.45,0:15:54.93,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Můžeš si věřit čemu chceš.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.33,0:15:59.48,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakonec ti, jejichž povinností je chránit 7³,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.48,0:16:04.73,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,a jsou propojení se 7³, Arcobalena, nemohou popřít to, co jsem právě řekl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:07.81,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Co— Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.81,0:16:09.51,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,C-co se to děje?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.02,0:16:11.99,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Reborne, vy jste v tom nějak zapojení?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.40,0:16:20.00,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Počkejte chvíli, nerozumím co to vlastně říkáte...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.38,0:16:21.60,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím vysvětlete víc...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:24.49,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Tato diskuze je u konce. Nechám zbytek na vás.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.49,0:16:25.19,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Ano, pane.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.19,0:16:25.96,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.65,0:16:31.01,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawado Tsunayoshi, odevzdej tvůj Vongolský Prsten Oblohy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.01,0:16:35.34,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Jestli to neuděláš, můžeš dát sbohem svým Strážcům.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.14,0:16:39.98,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Jestli vdechnete jenom minimum tohoto plynu, nevydržíte ani vteřinu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:41.98,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Počkej, Irie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.16,0:16:48.05,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Náš rozhovor ještě není u konce, s jednou částí, kterou řekls nesouhlasím.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.03,0:16:52.28,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Neztrácejte zbytečně náš čas.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:54.16,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemáte právo rozhodovat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.56,0:16:57.54,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Tohle je příkaz, ne vyjednávání.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.54,0:17:05.00,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Odevzdej svůj Vongolský Prsten Nebe do tří vteřin. Jestli to neuděláš, tví strážci budou eliminováni.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:06.71,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,P-počkejte chvíli!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:09.31,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Vy jste z Cervello, že?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.31,0:17:12.38,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Řekněte mi, proč pracujete pro Millefiore?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.38,0:17:13.22,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Tři.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.42,0:17:16.89,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Zatracená ženská!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.42,0:17:20.89,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeti si myslíš, že nás můžeš použít jako rukojmí, tak se pleteš!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.36,0:17:25.47,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Desátý nestarejte se o nás! Sundejte ty děvky!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.47,0:17:27.61,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,A-ale není žádný způsob. jak to udělat...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.61,0:17:29.07,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Dva.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.07,0:17:30.23,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Udělej to, Sawado!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:34.03,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Ikdyž jim dáš svůj Vongolský Prsten Nebe...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.03,0:17:35.99,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,...tak nás stejně zabijí!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.35,0:17:37.37,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,A-ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.37,0:17:39.38,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Desátý!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.38,0:17:40.70,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Nestarej se o nás!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:41.45,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Jedna!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.17,0:19:24.94,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi everyone, it's time for Haru's long-awaited "Haru Haru Interview Dangerous" segment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.94,0:19:28.56,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Our guest today is Bianchi-san, for her second appearance on this show.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.36,0:19:30.14,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Eek!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.99,0:19:33.92,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi~ \N Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.92,0:19:35.63,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,What... \N What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.63,0:19:37.94,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,A mushroom. \N My present for Reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:40.99,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,A mushroom? \N Isn't it a little too big?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.99,0:19:43.07,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's about two meters tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.07,0:19:44.63,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,It's three meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.63,0:19:48.65,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Eek! This is no longer the size of a normal mushroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.65,0:19:50.01,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cute, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.55,0:19:54.53,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than saying it's cute, I would say it looks pretty dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.53,0:19:55.84,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I the only one that thinks that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.28,0:19:58.21,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the name of this mushroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.63,0:20:00.68,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-ke da-ke ta-ke-ra da-ka ta-ke-o.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.68,0:20:03.14,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-ke da-ka ta-ke da-ka...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:06.42,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong, it's ke-da-ke da-ke-no ke-da-ke da-ka-yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.42,0:20:09.63,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Ke-da-ke da-da-ke-da... ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.63,0:20:11.35,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,I bit my tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:16.80,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Bianchi, the name you gave the \N first time was different than the second.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.80,0:20:18.36,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't bully her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.11,0:20:20.78,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just teasing her a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:23.15,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't tease me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.15,0:20:25.79,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,So what is the real name of this mushroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.79,0:20:27.44,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazon huge mushroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.44,0:20:28.28,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Eek!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.28,0:20:29.89,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,It's named based on its appearance?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.89,0:20:33.15,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Based on the name, you got it from the Amazon?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.15,0:20:34.67,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it was tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.05,0:20:40.01,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Bianchi's hobby is to travel the world to gather all kinds of poisonous items.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:41.21,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Poison?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.21,0:20:43.25,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just say poison?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.25,0:20:45.18,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Got a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:50.02,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. As long as we don't eat it, there's no problem, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.61,0:20:53.72,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought it here because I'd like Reborn to taste it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.72,0:20:55.31,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.72,0:20:57.07,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.07,0:20:59.58,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,That's cruel, Reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.58,0:21:03.12,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you said it's poisonous, I doubt anyone would eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.12,0:21:07.08,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,You're stupid. If you cook it the right way, you can make love potions from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.08,0:21:08.20,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Love potions?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.20,0:21:11.08,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. If the person you like drinks its properly made soup,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.08,0:21:12.83,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be able to capture his heart immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.20,0:21:14.58,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.33,0:21:17.29,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,"Heart" in the Japanese language means heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.42,0:21:20.30,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean killing the heart in one strike?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.30,0:21:22.55,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mean that, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.55,0:21:24.09,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.09,0:21:27.35,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how do we go about making the soup?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.35,0:21:29.87,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Dice the mushroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.87,0:21:31.63,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Dice it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.63,0:21:35.47,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Then use 1024 types of herbs and bat's eyeballs and such
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.47,0:21:39.07,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,mixed with 564 different kinds of ingredients, and boil them together...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.43,0:21:40.57,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Very simple, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.57,0:21:42.53,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,It's crazily difficult!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.53,0:21:44.90,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, that's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.90,0:21:47.43,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.43,0:21:50.12,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,I have already prepared the finished product.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.12,0:21:50.91,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Eek!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.91,0:21:52.43,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,You are well prepared,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.43,0:21:54.87,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like those from real cooking programs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.87,0:21:56.75,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Who will be drinking it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.27,0:22:01.61,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, of course that would be... Tsuna-san... or Tsuna-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.61,0:22:03.46,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.94,0:22:05.61,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.61,0:22:07.41,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,So I brought Tsuna here as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.41,0:22:09.44,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing, Bianchi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.44,0:22:11.44,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's time to taste the soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.44,0:22:13.47,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't joke around.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.47,0:22:15.97,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard what you were talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.97,0:22:18.90,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't say that, Tsuna-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.90,0:22:20.23,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.23,0:22:21.90,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Haru, you haven't tried it yet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.90,0:22:22.98,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Eek!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.98,0:22:24.86,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a very strong rebuttal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.86,0:22:27.46,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,You are pretty stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.46,0:22:30.18,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,You should gladly eat food made by a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.18,0:22:31.71,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.71,0:22:33.84,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never eat your Poison Cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.84,0:22:35.74,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd say that,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.44,0:22:40.30,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,So I made a cut on the rope earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.66,0:22:42.63,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Eek!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.63,0:22:43.63,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Ts-Tsuna-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.63,0:22:46.67,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like food poisoning. \N Send him to the hospital immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.67,0:22:50.80,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,All good children should never eat \N any suspicious-looking mushrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.80,0:22:53.26,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuna-san! Tsuna-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.80,0:22:53.26,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Say that earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.67,0:22:56.83,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Looks like the matter has become pretty serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.83,0:23:00.19,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to hurry and pay Tsuna-san a visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.19,0:23:02.90,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,So Haru's "Haru Haru Interview Dangerous" segment is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.27,0:23:05.38,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,See you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.38,0:23:09.69,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a mushroom soup that can neutralize all kinds of food poisoning. It's very suitable for a hospital visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.69,0:23:11.21,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,Please teach me how to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.21,0:23:12.91,hitman,,0000,0000,0000,,She never learns.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.96,0:17:54.93,Eng2,,0000,0000,0000,,Gazing at a smile for me, a smile for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:58.30,Eng2,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, it was sparkling for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.68,0:18:09.19,Eng2,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this every day can become special.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.32,0:18:19.20,Eng2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,0)}With the flower of love in my right pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:26.16,Eng2,,0000,0000,0000,,Once again I'm in your right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:29.75,Eng2,,0000,0000,0000,,Drawn out of town to Circus Town,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:32.84,Eng2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where light and shadows go up and down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.13,0:18:41.80,Eng2,,0000,0000,0000,,Together let's dash through it
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:46.65,Eng2,,0000,0000,0000,,To the goal step by step step by step
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.85,0:18:56.16,Eng2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind if it's little by little, your pace is perfectly fine
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.70,0:19:00.45,Eng2,,0000,0000,0000,,Gazing at a smile for me, a smile for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:03.91,Eng2,,0000,0000,0000,,Look it's sparkling, for an instant,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.49,0:19:13.46,Eng2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}So every day can become special.
